<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NutriTrack - Contraseña Restablecida</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo img {
            width: 80px;
            height: auto;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #6dbd3c;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .success-icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            color: #6dbd3c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .login-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #6dbd3c;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .login-button:hover {
            background-color: #5aa030;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/85JwWGj/logo.png" alt="NutriTrack Logo">
            <h1>nutritrack</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="success-icon">✓</div>
        
        <h1>¡Contraseña Restablecida!</h1>
        
        <p>Tu contraseña ha sido actualizada correctamente.</p>
        <p>Ya puedes iniciar sesión con tu nueva contraseña.</p>
        

    </div>
</body>
</html>